						<div class="postbody">The cart in is mostly for the PowerPak though if it sounds a lot better I could use the same mod for my Castlevania 3 (JP) cart. The reason I wanted to record the PowerPak is that, even though the PowerPak does not use the original chips, it seems to do a better job of emulating them than FamiTracker.
