				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can't pass audio through a diode. It's a rectifier and only allows DC current to flow. And since audio signals consist of an AC current with varying frequency A diode only allows current to flow in one direction. So since AC requires the ability to flow in both directions you would get no audio output.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

